title: Dead Men Don't Count (Western, 1968) Anthony Steffen, Mark Damon | Full Movie

sources.title: Dead Men Don't Count (Western, 1968) Anthony Steffen, Mark Damon | Full Movie
sources.description:
Two gunmen ride into a town with a plan to collect a large unearned bounty but are caught up in the local war for land caused by the impending arrival of the railroad.

Original title: ¿Quién grita venganza? (1968) I morti non si contano (Italy)  
Also Known As: Dead Men Don't Count / Cry for Revenge (USA/UK) | Les pistoleros du Nevada (France) | L'homme du Nevada (France) | An den Galgen, Bastardo! (Germany) | Dois homens e uma arma (Portugal) | Duell i Blakstone Hill (Sweden) | Död Man Pratar Inte (Sweden) | Oi nekroi den metriountai (Greece) | La venganza de Garringo (Mexico) | Deus Como Pai e o Diabo Por Sócio (Brazil) | 荒野の死闘 (Japan)

This film is available in Italian & German audio options, And subtitles in many more! 
For the English version: https://youtu.be/TzT2c7H16kw


Director: Rafael Romero Marchent
Writers: Marco Leto, Vittorio Salerno
Stars: Anthony Steffen, Mark Damon, María Martín
Genre: Western
